text: Coastal Carolina Community College is a public community college in Jacksonville, North Carolina. Roughly eight thousand students are enrolled at the institution. It is also a satellite school of the University of North Carolina at Wilmington. ==External links== * Official website Category:North Carolina Community College System colleges Category:Universities and colleges accredited by the Southern Association of Colleges and Schools Category:Education in Onslow County, North Carolina Category:Buildings and structures in Onslow County, North Carolina Category:Two-year colleges in the United States
